{"tid":2367323,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Intel釋單代工CPU，台積電TSMC市值超越巴郡，成全球市值第十大企業","createTime":"2021-01-15T08:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T09:02:09.000Z","uid":109923,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ee4b68f14d089e763148e95cc8922ec7e63653e2","tid":2367323,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T08:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3DBjnZi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3DBjnZi.jpg&h=76e88de2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晶圓代工廠龍頭台積電股價越升越有，在上日（13日）更衝破600新台幣大關，高見605新台幣，換算下來，市值已經突破5600億美元，超越股神巴菲特旗下的巴郡的5469.9億美元，成為全球市值第十大的企業。<br />\n<br />\n截止昨日（13日）為止，全球市值前十大的企業分別為，蘋果、沙特阿美、微軟、亞馬遜、Google母公司Alphabet、Tesla、騰訊、Facebook、阿里巴巴。而巴菲特旗下的巴郡下滑到第11位。<br />\n<br />\n據台積電最新的第四季業績，單季稅後純利1428億新台幣，超市場預期的1369億新台幣，折合相當於395億港元，按年增23%，得益於收入增加和利潤率改善。期內，每股盈利5.51元新台幣，純利與每股盈利繼續創新高。<br />\n<br />\n此外，外資對台積電的前景十分樂觀，認為其有很大可能拿到Intel的大單。當中，花旗環球證券將台積電基本、樂觀情境目標價喊到670新台幣、702新台幣，居主要外資最高。"},{"pid":"b82bcddc21604f334178b65da811b66c42446441","tid":2367323,"uid":124180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T08:52:04.000Z","msg":"TSM gogogo!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f17a6f591ebb3145cc6b09e65417d1ce298363","tid":2367323,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T08:57:23.000Z","msg":"騰信同阿里，兩者響中國封鎖市場食人口紅利搞獨大<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48c07fcb14081a19a285876b3da55525d96cb5a","tid":2367323,"uid":109923,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"53f17a6f591ebb3145cc6b09e65417d1ce298363","tid":2367323,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T08:57:23.000Z","msg":"騰信同阿里，兩者響中國封鎖市場食人口紅利搞獨大<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:00:52.000Z","msg":"台灣企業靠技術實力<br />\n支那靠數十年貿易戰封殺外商養大自己企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藍絲廢老：美國發動貿易戰好賤格<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe44696ec0c22fd9c17053e97e221e4b4003ec0","tid":2367323,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:02:09.000Z","msg":"諗起退潮時..."}]}